blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個款好似唔好食，我擺咗三個鐘啱啱食咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食個飯都諗咁耐<br />\n你應該同我一樣<br />\n平時好多野諗"},{"pid":"9904eec780c45ac91ffba00d6af0f5191f15127f","tid":503770,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早知去食越南河，買咗個美心飯但唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個款好似唔好食，我擺咗三個鐘啱啱食咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食個飯都諗咁耐<br />\n你應該同我一樣<br />\n平時好多野諗</blockquote><br />\n唔係，我頭先喺梳化瞓著咗咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f39000de5357e5529f48b30ce8fe873cbcdd68e","tid":503770,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"開名啦，中出巴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fbd3dcacd2cc89f8ac2ceb85238d1325e668f3","tid":503770,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開名啦，中出巴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n越蘆"},{"pid":"23c8a4b9da07e6d234d72ee244231cd74f6c35fa","tid":503770,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:54:14.000Z","msg":"咁少 起碼要食兩碗先夠飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8e013d10136da65e81bd901bfcff19b71c0439","tid":503770,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影得靚定本身靚</blockquote><br />\n係樓豬樣靚😍"},{"pid":"62e3138aff40ec0fe9c0bbe6b67da18199e950c6","tid":503770,"u